body_html: Again, 'Invalid handle to Interpreter' means you failed to create a valid model interpreter with the given model file. Please run your model with the most recently updated tf lite in Github, then post the exceptions here. The updated tf lite should throw exceptions when it fails to create a valid model interpreter with more detailed messages.
